description.content:
I will develop modern and responsive website with custom admin panel in php laravel.


My Services:

  • Custom coded according to your requirements.
  • Admin panel to manage website.
  • API development for mobile app.

why choose me?

  • I bring a wealth of knowledge and skills in web development, including proficiency in various frameworks and programming languages.
  • I am committed to delivering high-quality, tailor-made solutions that align with your project goals.
  • I understand the importance of meeting deadlines, and I strive to complete projects promptly without compromising on quality.
  • I believe in open and transparent communication. I'll keep you updated on the progress of your project and am readily available to address any questions
  • Your satisfaction is my priority. I am dedicated to ensuring that you are thrilled with the results of our collaboration

What You Will Receive:

  • Professionally designed.
  • Admin panel.
  • Multi user login.
  • API for mobile app development.
  • I will host website on your domain hosting.
  • Extra fast delivery.

Please discuss the requirements before placing order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you host code on server?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I will host your code on your server. I will work on cpanel only, no ftp.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How much time to complete the development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Depends on your requirements. It normally takes 3 days to 2 weeks.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you design the UI of website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I will design the user interface of the web application as well.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Admin panel will be mobile responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, both website and admin panel will be complete mobile responsive.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will admin panel work for blog website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can develop complete admin panel for blogs and news website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can we add it to Ecommerce website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. It will be perfect for multi vendor Ecommerce website with multiple login accounts.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many payment methods will be integrated?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: How can order how much methods you like. stripe, paypal or any other payment gateway.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can we manage gallery albums and static pages?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes you can manage gallery images and static pages with custom admin panel as well.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is difference between a CMS and custom admin panel?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: With CMS and website builders, there is large of unnecessary stuff. while with custom admin panel we will add only required features. It is custom coded and optimized. No external plugins.
